        <div>
                <h1>Hospital-based inpatient psychiatric services: the percentage of patients admitted to a hospital-based inpatient psychiatric setting who are screened within the first three days of admission for all of the following: risk of violence to self or others, substance use, psychological trauma history and patient strengths.</h1>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- /.content-header-meta -->

